OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud soon lifting to
OL,6,Fleave a fine day. After a cool start,
OL,7,Fsoon feeling warm with plenty of
OL,8,Fstrong April sunshine despite a breeze
OL,9,Fnear coasts and hills. Sunshine could
OL,10,Fturn hazy into the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome cloud returning to the
OL,13,Ffar east and on high ground. Otherwise
OL,14,Fa mostly clear night for all with
OL,15,Fbrisk winds on higher hills. A patchy
OL,16,Ffrost in the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
